Class IntegerBound

  • java.lang.Object
    • prism.IntegerBound

  • public class IntegerBound
extends java.lang.Object
    Canonical representation of an integer bound, with strict/non-strict lower and upper bound.

        Create new bounds.
        Parameters:
        lower: - The lower bound, null represents "no lower bound"
        lower_strict: - Is the lower bound strict (> lower) or non-strict (>= lower)
        upper: - The upper bound, null represents "no upper bound"
        upper_strict: - Is the upper bound strict (< upper) or non-strict (<= upper)

    • Method Detail

      • fromExpressionTemporal

        public static IntegerBound fromExpressionTemporal(ExpressionTemporal expression,
                                                  boolean check)
                                           throws PrismException
        Extract the bounds from an ExpressionTemporal expression and create the corresponding IntegerBound. Expects that constants for the upper and lower bounds have already been resolved. If check is true, throws an exception for negative or empty bounds.
        Parameters:
        expression - the expression
        check - check for non-negative bounds / non-emptiness?
        Returns:
        the IntegerBound for the expression
        Throws:
        PrismException

      • fromExpressionTemporal

        public static IntegerBound fromExpressionTemporal(ExpressionTemporal expression,
                                                  Values constantValues,
                                                  boolean check)
                                           throws PrismException
        Extract the bounds from an ExpressionTemporal expression and create the corresponding IntegerBound, resolving constants via constantValues. If check is true, throws an exception for negative or empty bounds.
        Parameters:
        expression - the expression
        constantValues - the values for constants (may be null)
        check - check for non-negative bounds / non-emptiness?
        Returns:
        the IntegerBound for the expression
        Throws:
        PrismException
